(- binary_sha3_384) Tj
T*
(- version-bound digest) Tj
T*
(- exact const.py pin values to update \(FALCONCLI_PINNED_VERSION_DIGESTS_BY_PLATFORM and) Tj
T*
(FALCONCLI_EXPECTED_HASH_BY_PLATFORM\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Prerequisites by OS) Tj
T*
(**Linux \(Debian/Ubuntu\)**) Tj
T*
(- build-essential \(gcc/g++/make\)) Tj
T*
(- cmake \(if you rebuild beyond the provided script\)) Tj
T*
(- libssl-dev \(for hashing/crypto\)) Tj
T*
(- Python 3.11+ and pip install -r requirements.txt) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**macOS**) Tj
T*
(- Xcode Command Line Tools: xcode-select --install) Tj
T*
(- Homebrew packages \(if needed\): brew install openssl cmake \(adjust PATH/CPPFLAGS/LDFLAGS for) Tj
T*
(OpenSSL if non-system\)) Tj
T*
(- Python 3.11+ and pip install -r requirements.txt) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(**Windows**) Tj
T*
(- Recommended: WSL \(Ubuntu\) with the Linux prerequisites above.) Tj
T*
(- Native \(more work\): install Visual Studio Build Tools \(C++ workload\) or MSYS2/MinGW-w64;) Tj
T*
(ensure gcc/clang and make are on PATH. Python 3.11+ with pip, and pip install -r) Tj
T*
(requirements.txt.) Tj
T*
(- PowerShell/WSL tip: use WSL to avoid toolchain headaches; Docker Desktop can build for you) Tj
T*
(\(see below\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Building falcon_cli from source) Tj
T*
(Falcon sources live in Src/Falcon/Falcon/. The Dockerfile builds with gcc by default.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Linux / macOS) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Notes:) Tj
T*
(- The script builds with -O3 -std=c99 -Wall -Wextra -DFALCON_FPNATIVE.) Tj
T*
(- Set FALCON_USE_AVX2=true on x86_64 with AVX2 support; keep false on ARM/older CPUs.) Tj
T*
(- After build, ensure falcon_cli is executable: chmod +x falcon_cli.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Windows \(WSL recommended\)) Tj
T*
(- **WSL path:** follow Linux steps above.) Tj
T*
(- **Native:** open MSYS2/MinGW shell or Developer Command Prompt, and compile with your) Tj
T*
(toolchain:) Tj
T*
(- MinGW example: gcc -O3 -std=c99 -Wall -Wextra -DFALCON_FPNATIVE -o falcon_cli cli.c falcon.c) Tj
T*
(fft.c fpr.c keygen.c rng.c shake.c sign.c vrfy.c common.c codec.c) Tj
T*
(- Adjust flags for AVX2: add -mavx2 -DFALCON_AVX2 if supported.) Tj
T*
(- Ensure falcon_cli.exe ends up in Src/Falcon/Binaries/windows-x86_64/ \(or set) Tj
T*
(ATHO_FALCONCLI_BIN\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
