T*
(Building and running via Docker \(simpler, all OS\)) Tj
T*
(If local toolchain setup is painful, let Docker build everything:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The Dockerfile installs build tools and runs the Falcon build as part of the image build. You) Tj
T*
(can then run the nodes via docker compose up ... without touching local compilers.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Common issues and fixes) Tj
T*
(- **AVX2 on unsupported CPUs:** remove -mavx2 -DFALCON_AVX2 \(set FALCON_USE_AVX2=false\) to avoid) Tj
T*
(illegal instruction errors.) Tj
T*
(- **Missing OpenSSL headers \(Linux/macOS\):** install libssl-dev \(Linux\) or brew install openssl) Tj
T*
(and set CPPFLAGS/LDFLAGS to point to it.) Tj
T*
(- **Permissions:** after building, run chmod +x falcon_cli.) Tj
T*
(- **Path issues \(Windows native\):** ensure your compiler and make are on PATH; prefer WSL to) Tj
T*
(simplify.) Tj
T*
(- **Python deps:** always pip install -r requirements.txt in a venv before running Python) Tj
T*
(scripts.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Verifying the build) Tj
T*
(- Run ./falcon_cli in Src/Falcon/Falcon to check it executes.) Tj
T*
(- Run .venv/bin/python Src/Falcon/Falcon/install_platform_binary.py to place the binary in the) Tj
T*
(platform directory and generate pin values.) Tj
T*
(- Update Constants.FALCONCLI_PINNED_VERSION_DIGESTS_BY_PLATFORM /) Tj
T*
(Constants.FALCONCLI_EXPECTED_HASH_BY_PLATFORM for release pinning \(legacy global pin remains) Tj
T*
(fallback-only\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Notes) Tj
T*
(- These steps are for advanced users; Docker/Compose is the easiest path to get a working) Tj
T*
(falcon_cli and nodes without local toolchain setup.) Tj
T*
(- Rebuild the image \(docker compose build --no-cache\) after changing Falcon sources or compiler) Tj
T*
(flags.) Tj
T*
